Setting Temporary Path

SET PATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.8.0_261\bin

Setting the permanent path

Step 1: Go to my computer or my pc 

Step 2: Right-click Go to Properties

step 3: Click on Advanced System Settings

Step 4: Click on Advanced Tab

Step 5: Click on Environment variable

Step 6: Click on the New tab in the User variable

Step 7: Assign value JAVA_HOME to variable Name

Step 8 : Assign C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.8.0_261\bin to variable value 

Step 9: Click OK Button
